In terms of “Spatial Data”, Liberia Institute of Statistics and Geo-Information Services (LISGIS) is the public agency responsible for the collection of statistical and geographic information that are used to produce maps."&nbsp;
However, entity(ies) whose business requires the collection of data are required to register and receive the requisite permit/license from the government entity controlling/overseeing the sector in which the entity(ies) would be conducting business. Every permit/license issued by the requisite government authority is renewable.Last modified 21 Feb 2022
				
			